===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act of [[abdicating]]; the [[renunciation]] of a high office, dignity, or trust, by its [[holder]]; commonly the voluntary renunciation of sovereign power; as, '''abdication''' of the throne, government, power, authority.

